===Pronunciation===
קדר / qêdâr / kay-dawr' 

===Etymology===
From {{HH|6937}}; 

===Adjective===
'''קדר'''

# dusky (of the skin or the tent); 

===Proper noun===
'''קדר'''

# Kedar, a son of Ishmael; also (collectively) bedawin (as his descendants or representatives): - Kedar.

